{"tid":722391,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做男人係咪唔應該太痴身","createTime":"2018-06-29T12:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T14:35:15.000Z","uid":131980,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ed1be40a989f41c278ce395885d42a0d400c88","tid":722391,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:49:40.000Z","msg":"做男人係咪唔應該太痴身?<br />\n<br />\n拍拖前我以為自己好獨立，拍拖後我完全變到成個女人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己太廢，太依賴佢，佔有慾強。自己日日都好唔開心。我覺得獨處時間太短了，今日得5分鐘到。我日日都好珍惜同佢獨處既時間，不過對佢尼講，可有可無。一大班人傾時我就變左個隱形人，係旁邊聽佢地傾計。<br />\n<br />\n佢係一個獨立能力強既女仔，我知係一件好事。現在呢個情況，我相信時間耐左所有野都會變好<br />\n<br />\n一個月都未過，完全無熱戀既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日心情都係過山車。<br />\n<br />\n講完了，純粹想講下自己好想對方同自己一齊經歷要有異性無人性果個階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話，我自己感覺到呢個係因果關係。"},{"pid":"a4f357ca61a6a820f17d0543a3cf9e6d5b111ae2","tid":722391,"uid":17123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:51:38.000Z","msg":"你仲賤過隻鴨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80763b12b59fe445375284cc588a6a25e1900f1b","tid":722391,"uid":88723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8b713d5efc8d29971dcc074b25ffea4aea7b3c","tid":722391,"uid":63950,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbe8656a213aaa0283c5459b43a786efcc2c6ce0","tid":722391,"uid":6445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:56:44.000Z","msg":"相處問題，睇下大家肯唔肯就大家，唔肯嘅話你都幾辛苦<br />\n<br />\n利申我就係咁玩完"},{"pid":"66a65e30ef8bdc5b45c420e6c22b5b9a79d0fd6b","tid":722391,"uid":134975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"問題係因為你世界得佢 但佢世界有好多人 <br />\n揾翻d興趣